name: Incident at Warehouse 51
description:
September 2034, a shipment of Titan branded robots enter warehouse 51 when a local EMP goes off hyperactivating their circuits turning them hostile. Corporate wants you to get your tin commander out into the warehouse and stop the attack immediately!
